com.kstechnologies.nirscannanolibrary

Class KSTNanoSDK.NanoGATT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kstechnologies.nirscannanolibrary.KSTNanoSDK.NanoGATT
  • Enclosing class:
    KSTNanoSDK

    public static class KSTNanoSDK.NanoGATT
extends java.lang.Object
    Collection of UUIDs for all of the GATT characteristics available on the Nano. NOTE: Some UUIDs will appear twice during enumeration because it is both write and notify, and has two instances in the GATT table for a single UUID
